channel.title: Axoloti Users in/around Vienna (Austria)
channel.description: Just got my core board. WOW! I am on a quest to use it as a stand-alone synth for my Seaboard Rise 25. I am not faint of heart, but also not a wizzard with the soldering iron, so if there are other folks around Vienna, Austria, who would like to work on Axoloti related stuff together, let's get in touch! First item on the agenda will be to make an enclosure with pots, and maybe some sort of display...
